CustomField.description: Do Not Insert - Prevents edits if the edit would result in a duplicate. Report Duplicate - Create a duplicate warning and allow the edited data to be saved. Do Nothing - Take no action.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Do Not Insert - Prevents edits if the edit would result in a duplicate. Report Duplicate - Create a duplicate warning and allow the edited data to be saved. Do Nothing - Take no action.
CustomField.label: Match on Update Result
